Package Model

Class Cab

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Cab
  • public class Cab
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains necessary data of a taxi. Takes care of declaring, initializing, saving its values and being able to obtain them or setting all its cab attributes.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Cab

        public Cab​(java.lang.String brand,
           java.lang.String model,
           java.lang.String licensePlate,
           boolean availability)
        This constructor method of Cab, initialize the attributes in base to all parameters. Initializes the driver but makes it null, because we will assign a driver to it in another class. Initializes a list of taxi trips, they are the trips that the taxi completes.
        Parameters:
        brand - the name of the cab brand.
        model - the name of the cab model.
        licensePlate - the license Plate of the car.
        availability - the state of accessibility the cab, if the cab is available, can be assigned to a customer, otherwise no.
